Detailed Description

Definitions of enumerals (members of enumerated types).

C++

  • example: 
    enum Enumeration
{
    FOO,        // this->value = NULL, identifierName = "FOO", definitionType = NULL
    BAR = 10    // this->value = "10", identifierName = "BAR", definitionType = NULL
};
